Title:The Calculations It Took to Become a Finance Chief
Author:Emily Glazer
Publication date:2021-10-30 00:00:00
------
In Personal Board of Directors, top business leaders talk about the people they turn to for advice, and how those people have shaped their perspective and helped them succeed. Previous installments from the series are here. Becoming a chief financial officer wasn’t on Robin Washington’s radar while growing up near Detroit. She achieved it twice as an adult. Now she wants to help other women and minorities reach positions of corporate power, too.  Becoming a chief financial officer wasn’t on Robin Washington’s radar while growing up near Detroit. She achieved it twice as an adult. Now she wants to help other women and minorities reach positions of corporate power, too. 